gout.title: Gout
gout.summary: Gout is a kind of arthritis caused by a buildup of uric acid crystals in the joints.  Gout, get out!Source: WebMD

goiter.title: Goiter
goiter.summary: (not to be confused with gout )  Goiter is not a kind of arthritis caused by a buildup of uric acid crystals in the joints.  Goiter, get out!Source: WebMD
